        <div class="reviewText stacked">
                  <em>
                    This review has been hidden because it contains spoilers. To view it,
                    <a href="#" onclick="Effect.toggle(&#39;reviewTextContainer1655990058&#39;); return false;">click here.</a>
                  </em>
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1655990058" class="readable"
                    style="display:none"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11234762713791154235">Loved it! Humorous, doesn’t tip toe around and is full on Roald Dahl! <br/><br/>I love the illustrations a lot, but don’t look for pretty! Look for exactly what the story is talking about. It can be kinda gross, but interesting and really challenges illustration. They are for more than just the “pretty”. <br/> <br/>My favorite moral, besides help one another? <br/><br/>If you act ugly and behave ugly, it makes you ugly and that is all! Otherwise you are fine and I love that !!! <br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


